---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section
  class="relative overflow-hidden bg-theme-blue text-white animate-fade-in-up pt-30 pb-10 md:py-30 inset-shadow-xl border-t-theme-gold border-t-6"
>
  <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 h-full md:w-1/2 opacity-70">
    <Image
      src="/orient-bambino.webp"
      alt="reloj-orient-bambino"
      class="object-cover md:h-full w-full object-center lg:object-right md:mask-r-to-100% md:mask-r-from-50% md:mask-b-from-90% mask-b-from-30%"
      loading="lazy"
      width={950}
      height={535}
    />
  </div>
  <div
    data-type="background-grid"
    class="absolute w-full md:w-1/2 bottom-0 right-0 top-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_left,#f9f7f22e_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#f9f7f22e_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:3rem_2rem] [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_50%_at_50%_0%,#000_70%,transparent_100%)]"
  >
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto w-full">
    <div class="max-w-3xl ml-auto pl-6">
      <h2
        class="text-4xl font-light leading-tight md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-500"
      >
        Sistema de <span class="text-theme-gold italic">Apartados</span>
      </h2>
      <p
        class="mt-12 md:mt-10 text-lg text-white/80 animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-700"
      >
        En Tiempo Noble, ofrecemos un sistema de apartados que te permite
        adquirir el reloj de tus sueños con facilidad. <br /> Aparta tu reloj favorito
        con un 20% del valor total y te lo enviaremos tan pronto como liquides el
        resto en plazo de 30 días. ¡Haz tu sueño realidad hoy mismo!
      </p>
      <button
        class="bg-theme-blue text-theme-gold border-2 border-theme-gold shadow-[2px_2px_0px_#DAC8A4] hover:shadow-none hover:translate-x-[2px] hover:translate-y-[2px] transition-all px-4 py-2 rounded-2xl mt-10 md:mt-6 cursor-pointer font-medium animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-700"
        onclick="window.location.href='/catalog'"
        type="button"
      >
        Explorar Catálogo
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
